    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎣 Dive into the Ultimate Real VR Fishing Experience!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore stunningly realistic environments with Real VR Fishing. Relax in 40 beautiful maps and expand your adventure with DLC packs, unlocking 95 fishing locations. Discover 150+ fish species in the base game and over 300 species with DLC content. Whether you’re a seasoned angler or a beginner, enjoy the peaceful ambiance and improve your skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >👥 Solo or Multiplayer (Up to 4 Players)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fish alone or join friends in multiplayer. Share the thrill, chat in real-time, and enjoy fishing together. Real VR Fishing is more than a game—it’s a space to bond and unwind.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💬 What Players Are Saying:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;Real VR Fishing is my go-to escape—like a vacation in VR.&quot; – Shroo****</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;Breathtaking visuals, and the multiplayer makes sharing the joy of fishing easy.&quot; – squir***</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >These reviews show why players love Real VR Fishing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏆 Award-Winning &amp; Constantly Updated</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Voted Facebook Oculus Game of the Year 2019, Real VR Fishing offers monthly updates and seasonal events, adding new challenges and fish to catch.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✨ Customize, Progress, and Master Fishing</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Level up, unlock rare fish, and customize your avatar and aquarium. Whether you start in Normal Mode or aim for Expert Mode, find new ways to enjoy VR fishing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎧 Fish, Stream, and Multitask</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Listen to music, watch videos, or browse the web while fishing using the built-in web browser. It’s the perfect way to unwind.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💥 Download Now and Start Your VR Adventure!</p>",
